==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: doggoned
<hw>dog"goned</hw></mhw> <pr>(?)</pr>,
<pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Euphemism from <ets>God-damned</ets>.]</ety>
<def>Damned; confounded; -- used as an expression of displeasure;
<as>as, I wish those <ex>doggone</ex> telemarketers would quit calling
at suppertime</as>.</def> <mark>[Informal]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>doggoned</ent>⟦br⟧
<ent>doggone</ent>⟦br⟧
